{"tid":1786906,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湖北少女色誘洋漢 夥黨掠財物","createTime":"2019-12-17T13:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T13:37:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d43f0bd16568172e11649ee704792dd6e04eef9c","tid":1786906,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191217/GNFTCE2DAN5DQ4Z76JEF6OQAQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191217%2FGNFTCE2DAN5DQ4Z76JEF6OQAQA%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0rV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=cba91555\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191217%2FGNFTCE2DAN5DQ4Z76JEF6OQAQA%2F&h=6df23667\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191217/GNFTCE2DAN5DQ4Z76JEF6OQAQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n湖北少女色誘洋漢 夥黨掠財物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191217/large/1576513660_0634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576513660_0634.jpg&h=8c8376ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑犯被黑布蒙頭押走。 鄭大康攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】17歲少女在旺角彌敦道近旺角道「獵食」，兜搭獨行的56歲外籍男，訛稱提供按摩甚至性服務，引領對方到附近彌敦道737號金輪大廈一間公寓，然後聯同三名男同黨偷去事主所有財物後速逃，引起早在現場埋伏的警員可疑，上前截查，分別在兩名男同黨身上搜獲屬於外籍男子的信用卡、現金及房卡，警方將四人拘捕，通宵扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警埋伏拉人<br />\n<br />\n被捕三男一女分別來自湖北、廣東及河南，數日前持旅遊證件來港，警方相信他們是犯罪集團骨幹成員。由於旺角近期發生多宗盜竊案，犯案團夥以女同黨在街上兜搭年紀成熟的男士，以提供按摩甚至性服務色誘對方到附近廉價賓館或公寓。入房間後女同黨即叫受害人除下財物後沖涼，乘事主沖涼時，通知男同黨入房偷走事主所有財物，然後一同逃去。旺角警區刑事情報科人員分析近期多宗同類案件後鎖定多個犯案黑點，派員埋伏監視。<br />\n<br />\n昨午約3時，17歲湖北少女在彌敦道金輪大廈以同一手法犯案，與三名男同黨（22至40歲）得手離開時，被在場埋伏的警員截查，警員在其中兩名男同黨身上搜獲屬於受害人的信用卡、4,000元現金及一張房卡，將四人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭大康"},{"pid":"8f8c951008d368fe0cbfa76fc7dba2062c7c59a2","tid":1786906,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"湖北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c966ec95f5d0354c22d3a7ec21136ea41aaea5c1","tid":1786906,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}